* Spawn time-consuming operations (such as Search) and proxy back the result
  to the view in the main-loop.
  
* Handle login/logout in a better fashion. Should be a way of logging out
  and switching accounts etc.
  
* Enable purchase of multiple songs at one time. And albums.

